{"tid":1518004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保皇黨：有研究指蒙面者較暴力 應盡快制定禁蒙面法","createTime":"2019-08-30T06:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:07:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ab06db42a757292169de0b104fae0cf37ed5121f","tid":1518004,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯、工聯會促政府盡快制定禁蒙面法，又引研究指蒙面者的暴力程度較沒蒙面者高</span>。公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋今日表示，如果蒙面者就暴力程度高，<span style=\"color: red;\">有關邏輯亦應用在警方上</span>，指現時警員行為愈來愈為人詬病，認為建制派和政府與其考慮一些「旁門左道」的蒙面法，不如從政治上解決問題，又說蒙面和戴口罩屬個人權利，<span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面法本身在西方社會已備受爭議和法律挑戰</span>。<br />\n<br />\n就政府被指有意引用《緊急情況規例條例》(《緊急法》)，楊岳橋又表示此法是剝奪香港人應有的權利，稱如果政府引用此舉會令外國撤資，對香港情況失去信心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e6%8c%87%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e8%80%85%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e9%ab%98-%e6%a5%8a%e5%b2%b3%e6%a9%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%90%8c%e6%a8%a3%e6%87%89%e7%94%a8%e5%9c%a8%e8%ad%a6%e6%96%b9-186960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%258c%2587%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b%25e9%25ab%2598-%25e6%25a5%258a%25e5%25b2%25b3%25e6%25a9%258b%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%2587%2589%25e7%2594%25a8%25e5%259c%25a8%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%2596%25b9-186960&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUinWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=5aecb63a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e6%8c%87%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e8%80%85%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e9%ab%98-%e6%a5%8a%e5%b2%b3%e6%a9%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%90%8c%e6%a8%a3%e6%87%89%e7%94%a8%e5%9c%a8%e8%ad%a6%e6%96%b9-186960</a>"},{"pid":"6842136fc0abd2d4c1fceb3e437986e0b7f69890","tid":1518004,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj